I"Ì<p>On January 11th, the day after David Bowie died, The New York Public Library‚Äôs blog posted <a href="http://www.nypl.org/blog/2016/01/11/david-bowies-top-100-books?hspace=332034">a list of the musician‚Äôs 100 favorite books</a>, based off of <a href="https://www.facebook.com/davidbowie/?target_post=10151603205477665&amp;ref=story_permalink">a Facebook post on his verified page from 2013</a>. A friend sent me the NYPL link and I, delighted by the idea of a project, looked up each of them on Amazon.</p>

